snippet.title: Celebrity Craze
snippet.description:
This Channel intends to provide the most breaking celeb news, drama and controversies all in one place. Also, information not only about Celebrities from Hollywood Film Industry but also Famous People around the World. We maintain different Playlists which you could come back and watch videos from your desired interest category. 

We also promise to keep our viewers entertained. Thanks for taking your time to checkout the Channel!

Subscribe to never miss a video.
